<section id="expandablelistview">
	<title>Implementing an expandable ListView</title>
	<section id="expandablelistview_concept">
		<title>ExpandableListView</title>
		<para>
			The
			<code>ExpandableListView</code>
			is similar to
			<code>ListView</code>	
			but allow you to define groups and details for this group.
			<code>ExpandableListView</code>
			expects
			and adapter of type
			<code>BaseExpandableListAdapter</code>
			.
		</para>
		<para>In this case you have to define two layouts, one for the group
			and another one for the details row.
		</para>
	</section>
	<section id="expandablelistview_example">
